Key Match Events: Brice Sensabaugh scored a game-high 27 points, including going 5-of-6 from 3-point range.
Pre-Game Insights: The Jazz were shorthanded due to injuries to Lauri Markkanen, Jordan Clarkson, Keyonte George, and John Collins.
Post-Match Reflections: Jazz head coach Will Hardy praised Brice Sensabaugh's consistency and confidence after scoring 27 points two nights in a row.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Brice Sensabaugh is from Orlando and played in front of his hometown crowd.
